# Account.TransferTo method

Creates a typical 2-split transaction.

```csharp
public void TransferTo(Account toAccount, GncNumeric fromAmount, GncNumeric toAmount, 
    DateOnly date, string description)
```

| parameter | description |
| --- | --- |
| fromAmount | Amount (positive) to withdraw from this account. |
| toAccount | The credit account. |
| toAmount | Amount to deposit. Defaults to fromAmount. |
| date | The date. Defaults to today. |
